text: Alison Murray Paterson (born 29 May 1966) is a British rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * (1991 World Championships} * (1992 Olympic Games) * * * Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:British female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Great Britain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Edinburgh
